data.title: Roger Birnbaum Productions
data.text:
Logo description by Hoa and Shadeed A. Kelly

Logo capture by EnormousRat

(1997-2007)

Nickname: The Pear

Logo: On a black background, we see a green pear that is designed to look like a fingerprint. Below it has the text ROGER BIRNBAUM with a line below it and the text PRODUCTIONS underneath.

Trivia: The logo is a pear because "Birnbaum" means "pear tree" in German.

FX/SFX: None.

Music/Sounds: None or the closing theme of the movie.

Availability: Can be seen at the end of RocketMan, Holy Man!, Six Days Seven Nights, Angels in the Infield, and the Rush Hour franchise.

Editor's Note: None.
